title: YOB - Discography 2000-2013 - FLAC
description:
Band: YOB
Country: USA
Genre: Sludge/Doom Metal
Quality: FLAC

Albums:
2000 - YOB (demo, MP3 320)
2002 - Elaborations of Carbon
2003 - Catharsis
2003 - Catharsis (remastered)
2004 - The Illusion of Motion
2005 - The Unreal Never Lived
2007 - Middian - Age Eternal
2009 - The Great Cessation
2011 - Atma
2011 - Live at Roadburn 2010

Catharsis is in two editions, original from 2003 and remastered from 2013. Please treat the demo (MP3 format) and Age Eternal as a bonus. I don't have access to lossless version of the demo. Middian is in fact a continuation of YOB under a new name, after the band broke up in 2005. In my opinion their only album should be included.
